        },
        {
            "name": "Performers",
            "type": "section",
            "sections": [
                {
                    "name": "Let's See A Show",
                    "type": "section",
                    "text": "Prices for a night's entertainment are per head and can be far higher for world-class performers. <b>Circus</b> 1 sp; <b>Dance</b> 2 cp social, 6 cp stage performance, 1 gp high-society ball; <b>Stage Play</b> 6 cp small theater, 1 sp major theater; <b>Opera</b> 5 gp general admission, 20 gp box seats; <b>Music</b> 5 cp troubadours, 2 sp orchestra; <b>Street Performance</b> tips of 1\u20132 cp.",
                    "sources": {
                        "type": "source",
                        "name": "Gamemastery Guide",
                        "link": {
                            "type": "link",
                            "name": "Gamemastery Guide pg. 236",
                            "alt": "Gamemastery Guide pg. 236",
                            "href": "https://paizo.com/products/btq01zq7"
                        },
                        "page": 236
                    },
                    "subtype": "sidebar",
                    "sidebar_type": "advice_and_rules",
                    "sidebar_heading": "Advice and Rules",
                    "image": "Sidebar_1_AdviceAndRules.png"
                }
            ],
            "text": "Performances can serve as entertainment, expressions of beauty, or part of a shared culture.",
